<template>
    <MDBFooter :text="['center', 'lg-start']">
        <MDBContainer class="p-4">
            <MDBRow>
                <MDBCol>
                    <router-link to='/' class="text-dark">Home</router-link>
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <router-link to='/gallery' class="text-dark">Gallery</router-link>
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <router-link to='/about' class="text-dark">About</router-link>
                </MDBCol>
                <MDBCol>
                    <router-link to='/contact' class="text-dark">Contact</router-link>
                </MDBCol>
            </MDBRow>
        </MDBContainer>
    </MDBFooter>
</template>

<script>
import {
    MDBFooter,
    MDBContainer,
    MDBRow,
    MDBCol
} from 'mdb-vue-ui-kit';

export default {
    components: {
        MDBFooter,
        MDBContainer,
        MDBRow,
        MDBCol
    },
};
</script>

<style>
.text-dark {
    font-size: 1.5rem !important;
}
</style>
